{"tid":1640051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"撕毀台大連儂牆 中國人李紹東強制出境 5年不得入境台灣","createTime":"2019-10-08T23:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T04:32:14.000Z","uid":41343,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"151db568289967d9892065c65de733b321ee0269","tid":1640051,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:33:35.000Z","msg":"中國來台自由行旅客李紹東撕毀台大連儂牆遭法辦後，移民署晚間將其強制出境並管制5年不得入境台灣。<br />\n<br />\n中國遊客李紹東前往台灣大學撕毀連儂牆標語，遭警方以現行犯移送並接受台北地檢署複訊後，今台北地檢署做出緩起訴處分並解除限制出境。<br />\n<br />\n移民署表示，由於李男行為違反我國法令規定，隨即對李男依法強制出境並管制5年內不得再入境。<br />\n<br />\n李男以自由行名義來台觀光，卻前往台灣大學連儂牆撕毀展版上展示各式海報，經台大學生會提起告訴，李男依毀損罪嫌移送臺北地方檢察署偵辦。<br />\n<br />\n移民署立即於當（7）天依大陸地區人民來台從事觀光許可辦法規定（有事實足認為有犯罪行為、從事與許可目不符之活動），廢止李男停留許可。現經台北地檢署作出緩起訴處分，依台灣地區與大陸地區人民關係條例第18條規定，強制李男出境並管制5年內不得再入境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2940819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2940819&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=f3193d37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2940819&h=1b69bbb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2940819</a>"},{"pid":"a025c1880973af399c47bf544d64e5a9984f5e8c","tid":1640051,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:48:29.000Z","msg":"全球排中"},{"pid":"35995089c79e63d398d4190c7e0aea238c41aecd","tid":1640051,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbdc54d0962371165a66ce1783a317966d87ff9","tid":1640051,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":